<BaseLayout title="Jinghao Wen — Personal Site">
<section class="page active" id="home">
  <div class="home-hero">
    <h1 class="home-greeting">
      <span class="en">Hi, I'm <em>Jinghao Wen</em> —<br>PhD student, bartender &amp; reader.</span>
      <span class="zh" style="display:none">你好，我是<em>文靖豪</em>——<br>博士研究生、调酒师与读者。</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="home-bio en">I am a PhD student in the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering, Villanova University, advised by Prof.<a href="https://vu-detail.github.io/people/jiao.html" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;"> Xun Jiao</a>. My current research interests lie in <strong>Machine Learning System</strong>, <strong>Robust AI</strong>, <strong>Efficient AI</strong> and <strong>Bio-inspired Computing</strong>.</p>
    <p class="home-bio zh" style="display:none">我是维拉诺瓦大学电子与计算机工程系博士研究生，导师为<a href="https://vu-detail.github.io/people/jiao.html" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">焦珣</a>教授。我目前的研究兴趣是<strong>机器学习系统</strong>，<strong>鲁棒人工智能</strong>，<strong>高效人工智能</strong>和<strong>生物启发计算</strong>。</p>
    <div class="home-links">
      <a class="btn btn-solid" href="mailto:jinghao.wen@outlook.com"><span class="en">Get in Touch</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">联系我</span></a>
      <a class="btn btn-out" href="/cv.pdf" target="_blank"><span class="en">Download CV</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">下载简历</span></a>
      <a class="btn btn-out" href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=HQxVjZEAAAAJ&hl=zh-CN" target="_blank"><span class="en">Google Scholar</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">谷歌学术</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-block">
    <h2 class="home-block-title"><span class="en">About Me</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">关于我</span></h2>
    <p class="home-body en">I am a PhD student in the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering, Villanova University, advised by Prof. <a href="https://vu-detail.github.io/people/jiao.html" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">Xun Jiao</a>. My current research interests lie in <strong>Machine Learning System</strong>, <strong>Robust AI</strong>, <strong>Efficient AI</strong> and <strong>Bio-inspired Computing</strong>. Overall research focuses on developing high-performant, energy-efficient, and robust-and-reliable AI/ML systems, using a cross-layer full-stack approach spanning hardware, software, and algorithm. I got my bachelor's degree from the School of Computer Science at Central China Normal University. During my undergraduate studies, I joined the Intelligent Robot Laboratory and, under the guidance of Prof. <a href="https://cs.ccnu.edu.cn/info/1111/1877.htm" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">Xi Peng</a>, engaged in projects and research related to embodied intelligence, human-computer interaction, and computer vision. In addition, I joined the SmartSystems Laboratory at the University of Florida. Under the guidance of Prof. <a href="https://www.ece.ufl.edu/people/faculty/christophe-bobda/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">Christophe Bobda</a>, I conducted research on intelligent embedded systems, intelligent sensing, and robotics technology. The focus was on runtime optimization, researching the design and runtime operation of high-performance adaptive architectures, and applying it to fields such as image processing, embedded optimization, security and control.
      <br><br>I firmly believe that people need a lasting inner drive to maintain curiosity, awe and respect for all people and things, whether they know or not, without losing rational thinking or emotional observation. This is not only about scientific research, but more importantly, about life. Therefore, beyond scientific research, I also try to keep myself perceiving and exploring life: to experience different lifestyles and get to know different people; Taste and document various foods (exploring nearly fifty restaurants in New York one after another); Obtained the bartender certificate in New York. Read books of different themes; Record the moments along the way with a camera during the trip. Pick up the guitar that has been forgotten for many years again; Even at one point, he tried to use tarot cards to peek into some unknowns - although it still seems absurd now...</p>
    <p class="home-body zh" style="display:none">我是维拉诺瓦大学电子与计算机工程系博士研究生，导师为<a href="https://vu-detail.github.io/people/jiao.html" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">焦珣</a>教授。我目前的研究兴趣是<strong>机器学习系统</strong>，<strong>鲁棒人工智能</strong>，<strong>高效人工智能</strong>和<strong>生物启发计算</strong>，总体研究重点是开发高性能、节能、稳健可靠的人工智能/机器学习系统，采用跨层全栈方法，涵盖硬件、软件和算法。我本科毕业于华中师范大学计算机学院，本科学习期间我加入智能机器人实验室，在<a href="https://cs.ccnu.edu.cn/info/1111/1877.htm" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">彭熙</a>教授的指导下从事具身智能、人机交互、计算机视觉相关的项目和研究。此外我还曾加入佛罗里达大学的智能系统实验室，在<a href="https://www.ece.ufl.edu/people/faculty/christophe-bobda/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;">Christophe Bobda</a>教授的指导下，从事智能嵌入式系统、智能传感和机器人技术的研究，重点在于运行时优化，研究高性能自适应架构的设计和运行时运行，并将其应用于图像处理、嵌入式优化、安全和控制等领域。
<br><br>我坚信人需要持久的内驱力，保持对一切或了解或不了解之人与物的好奇、敬畏、尊重，既不失理性的思考也不失感性的观照，不仅仅是对科研，更重要的是对生活。因而，在科研之外，我也试着让自己保持对生活的感知与探索：去体验不同的生活方式，认识不同的人；品尝与记录各式食物（在纽约陆续探索了近五十家餐厅）；考取了纽约的调酒师证书；阅读不同题材的书籍；在旅行途中用相机记录沿途的片刻；重新捡起遗忘多年的吉他；甚至一度也试图借助塔罗牌去窥探某些未知——虽然如今看来仍显得荒谬无比...</p>
